  %% Diagram 77: Revenue Waterfall and Reserve Allocation Flow

  Inflow[Gross platform inflows\nsubscriptions + commissions + addons]
  OpCost[Cover operating costs]
  Enough{Revenue >= operating costs?}

  Reserve[Allocate 20% reserve fund]
  Distributable[Compute distributable remainder]
  Report[Finance reporting and governance update]

  Shortfall[Revenue shortfall state]
  Control[Cost-control and spend-priority actions]
  Escalate[Executive finance escalation]

  Inflow --> OpCost --> Enough
  Enough -- Yes --> Reserve --> Distributable --> Report
  Enough -- No --> Shortfall --> Control --> Escalate
